text: Nahuel () is a male given name of Mapuche origin, nawel meaning jaguar. It is used in Argentina, Chile and Uruguay. ==Notable people named Nahuel== *Nahuel Moreno (1924–1987), Argentine politician *Nahuel Valentini (1988–), Argentine professional footballer *Nahuel Fioretto (1981–), Argentine professional footballer *Nahuel Guzmán (1986–), Argentine professional footballer *Nahuel Pérez Biscayart (1986–), Argentine actor *Nahuel Quiroga (1991–), Argentine professional footballer *Matías Nahuel (1996–), Argentine-Spanish professional footballer *Nahuel Bustos (1998–), Argentine professional footballer *Nahuel Ferraresi (1998–), Venezuelan professional footballer ==References== Category:Mapuche Category:Masculine given names Category:South American given names Category:Spanish masculine given names
title: Nahuel
